      "span_text": "For each specimen, the percentage of viable chondrocytes was calculated using a device with 25 points per field, analyzing 12 microscopic fields (original magnification ϫ400) for a total of 300 points for each cartilage segment [CITATION_1] ( Figure 1) ."
